divs: Sighting DetailsGoing through some google Earth Pics and there is a picture of a man walking in a desert climate, and in the sky, above the mountain, is a dark orb. It doesn't look like a bird or any aircraft I am familiar with. I reported this before and never got any response. Everytime I view the picture it puzzles me. I am attaching the photo. I put a location, time and date in the required fields on this form, but they are wrong since I was not there, I do not know the man in the photo and have no clue where he was or what the date and time were. I am sure I can find out though.
Summary: going through some google Earth photos and noticed an orb in the sky.
